this stupid grin on my face!

00:01:39.849 --> 00:01:41.017 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
I totally get it!

00:01:41.101 --> 00:01:42.977 position:50% align:center
It feels like you just
can't help but smile!

00:01:43.061 --> 00:01:44.145 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA] Well, we've
got plenty of time...

00:01:44.229 --> 00:01:45.605 position:50% align:center
[JUJU]
What is wrong with her?

00:01:45.689 --> 00:01:48.566 position:50% align:center
