for her outfit, right?

00:02:25.979 --> 00:02:27.230 position:50% align:center
I knew it.

00:02:27.313 --> 00:02:29.274 position:50% align:center
There are other
costs incurred here.

00:02:29.357 --> 00:02:32.318 position:50% align:center
Transportation, tools,
and props for example.

00:02:32.402 --> 00:02:33.695 position:50% align:center
I'll pay you back for it.

00:02:33.778 --> 00:02:35.030 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry.

