an allowance, so it's fine.

00:02:37.866 --> 00:02:39.034 position:50% align:center
[JUJU]
No, it's not.

00:02:39.117 --> 00:02:41.786 position:50% align:center
Good artists need
to be paid for their work.

00:02:43.163 --> 00:02:44.497 position:50% align:center
Thank you, though.

00:02:44.581 --> 00:02:48.126 position:50% align:center
For giving her such a
great experience today.

00:02:48.209 --> 00:02:50.253 position:50% align:center
Honestly, I had
no idea she loved Soma

00:02:50.337 --> 00:02:54.174 position:50% align:center
so much that she
wanted to cosplay him.

00:02:54.257 --> 00:02:55.592 position:50% align:center
It makes me wonder
why she felt like

00:02:55.675 --> 00:02:58.428 position:50% align:center
she had to hide it from me.

00:02:58.511 --> 00:03:01.723 position:50% align:center
I've failed her, I guess.

00:03:01.806 --> 00:03:03.933 position:50% align:center
You didn't do
anything wrong, Inui.

00:03:04.017 --> 00:03:05.852 position:50% align:center
I promise.

00:03:05.935 --> 00:03:07.187 position:50% align:center
It's just that...

00:03:07.270 --> 00:03:09.064 position:50% align:center
It takes a lot of
courage, you know?

00:03:09.147 --> 00:03:10.899 position:50% align:center
Telling others about
the things you love,

00:03:10.982 --> 00:03:12.484 position:50% align:center
things you want to try.

00:03:12.567 --> 00:03:15.737 position:50% align:center
It can be scary sometimes.

00:03:15.820 --> 00:03:17.655 position:50% align:center
I know how that feels.

00:03:18.990 --> 00:03:21.493 position:50% align:center
[JUJU] You took something
that's so precious to me.

00:03:21.576 --> 00:03:26.790 position:50% align:center
And you, you handled it with
such care and consideration.

00:03:26.873 --> 00:03:30.418 position:50% align:center
There's something about you.

00:03:30.502 --> 00:03:31.920 position:50% align:center
You're wonderful.

00:03:32.003 --> 00:03:33.338 position:50% align:center
Uh, did you say something?

00:03:33.421 --> 00:03:34.589 position:50% align:center
[JUJU]
Who me?

00:03:34.673 --> 00:03:35.882 position:50% align:center
Not a word.

00:03:38.426 --> 00:03:41.554 position:50% align:center
That's the last thing
I need you to hear.

00:03:41.638 --> 00:03:43.515 position:50% align:center
Perfect. Now turn this way.

00:03:43.598 --> 00:03:45.016 position:50% align:center
Slowly.

00:03:56.236 --> 00:03:58.405 position:50% align:center
I got the most gorgeous
shot of you just now!

00:03:58.488 --> 00:04:00.156 position:50% align:center
--F'real?
--Yes!

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:01.324 position:50% align:center
[fabric ripping]

00:04:01.408 --> 00:04:03.743 position:50% align:center
[MARIN] Hmm?
What was that noise?

00:04:05.662 --> 00:04:07.080 position:50% align:center
Whoa. Shinju?

00:04:07.163 --> 00:04:08.540 position:50% align:center
Uh. Not to make it awkward,

00:04:08.623 --> 00:04:11.042 position:50% align:center
but your bongos
are going bonkers.

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:18.508 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU screams]
Omigosh, my B-Holder just broke!

00:04:23.221 --> 00:04:26.433 position:50% align:center
All I had was the natural
light spill in the studio,

00:04:26.516 --> 00:04:28.935 position:50% align:center
but it ended up
working out perfectly.

00:04:29.019 --> 00:04:30.895 position:50% align:center
I really love this
shot in particular.

00:04:30.979 --> 00:04:31.771 position:50% align:center
[JUJU]
I agree.

00:04:31.855 --> 00:04:32.939 position:50% align:center
It looks great.

00:04:33.023 --> 00:04:34.649 position:50% align:center
She nailed the character.

00:04:34.733 --> 00:04:37.027 position:50% align:center
The outfit looks perfect on her.

00:04:37.110 --> 00:04:38.403 position:50% align:center
Yeah, it's nice.

00:04:38.486 --> 00:04:42.115 position:50% align:center
She brought more depth
than I expected her to.

00:04:42.198 --> 00:04:43.491 position:50% align:center
I thought I felt
love at first sight

00:04:43.575 --> 00:04:46.202 position:50% align:center
with the outfit
Wakana Gojo created.

00:04:46.286 --> 00:04:48.872 position:50% align:center
But I guess it was
about more than that.

00:04:53.793 --> 00:04:55.420 position:50% align:center
Did you like my cosplay?

00:04:55.503 --> 00:04:57.047 position:50% align:center
Or was it too weird for you?

00:04:57.130 --> 00:04:58.548 position:50% align:center
What? No, not at all!

00:04:58.631 --> 00:05:01.468 position:50% align:center
Why would you ask that?

00:05:01.551 --> 00:05:04.763 position:50% align:center
It's just that I could never
pull a cosplay like that off.

00:05:04.846 --> 00:05:05.805 position:50% align:center
So I'm in awe.

00:05:05.889 --> 00:05:08.266 position:50% align:center
Guess I got a
little jealous, too.

00:05:09.893 --> 00:05:11.227 position:50% align:center
[screams]

00:05:11.311 --> 00:05:12.687 position:50% align:center
Okay, what was that?

00:05:12.771 --> 00:05:14.356 position:50% align:center
Are you possessed or something?

00:05:14.439 --> 00:05:16.066 position:50% align:center
My whole world just
turned upside down!

00:05:16.149 --> 00:05:17.359 position:50% align:center
There's a cosplay
that you can't pull off,

00:05:17.442 --> 00:05:19.027 position:50% align:center
and you're jealous of me?

00:05:19.110 --> 00:05:20.570 position:50% align:center
What are you talking about?

00:05:20.653 --> 00:05:21.821 position:50% align:center
I'm human, too.

00:05:21.905 --> 00:05:23.031 position:50% align:center
Yeah, sure.

00:05:23.114 --> 00:05:24.783 position:50% align:center
But you always look
amazing in everything.

00:05:24.866 --> 00:05:26.826 position:50% align:center
[JUJU]
Nope. That's not true.

00:05:26.910 --> 00:05:28.286 position:50% align:center
I pick from the
characters I like

00:05:28.370 --> 00:05:31.289 position:50% align:center
that have the same shape
and size as I do, that's all.

00:05:31.373 --> 00:05:34.584 position:50% align:center
I mean, I'd love to cosplay
Black Lobelia or Soma, too.

00:05:34.668 --> 00:05:37.754 position:50% align:center
But they're tall characters
and it wouldn't look right.

00:05:37.837 --> 00:05:40.882 position:50% align:center
I don't want to wear
something that isn't perfect.

00:05:40.965 --> 00:05:43.301 position:50% align:center
It's not like I have low
self-esteem or something.

00:05:43.385 --> 00:05:46.012 position:50% align:center
It's just that sometimes I wish
I could change my appearance,

00:05:46.096 --> 00:05:48.765 position:50% align:center
or I feel like I could've
done things better.

00:05:49.891 --> 00:05:52.268 position:50% align:center
[JUJU] Like if I had a more
feminine figure like you,

00:05:52.352 --> 00:05:56.022 position:50% align:center
I could knock off so many
other cosplays on my wish list.

00:05:57.399 --> 00:05:58.817 position:50% align:center
And I'm sorry.

00:05:58.900 --> 00:06:00.944 position:50% align:center
I really am quite
jealous of you.

00:06:03.154 --> 00:06:04.322 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
My point was,

00:06:04.406 --> 00:06:06.658 position:50% align:center
we don't always know how
someone really feels.

00:06:06.741 --> 00:06:09.494 position:50% align:center
But, well,
we all have struggles.

00:06:11.621 --> 00:06:12.997 position:50% align:center
Here's the plan.

00:06:13.081 --> 00:06:15.667 position:50% align:center
When I'm in high school,
I'll get a job to save money.

00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:17.002 position:50% align:center
And then we can do it.

00:06:17.085 --> 00:06:18.712 position:50% align:center
Cosplay, together.

00:06:18.795 --> 00:06:19.796 position:50% align:center
Are you kidding me?

00:06:19.879 --> 00:06:20.714 position:50% align:center
Yes, please!

00:06:20.797 --> 00:06:21.840 position:50% align:center
Do you mean that, really?

00:06:21.923 --> 00:06:23.216 position:50% align:center
Uh-huh.

00:06:23.299 --> 00:06:24.801 position:50% align:center
[JUJU] I spent way
too much money this time,

00:06:24.884 --> 00:06:28.680 position:50% align:center
so it might take a
minute to save up again.

00:06:28.763 --> 00:06:30.598 position:50% align:center
But once I do,

00:06:30.682 --> 00:06:33.018 position:50% align:center
I'm gonna take a break
from group cosplay.

00:06:33.101 --> 00:06:34.310 position:50% align:center
I definitely learned

00:06:34.394 --> 00:06:36.646 position:50% align:center
that I prefer doing
photoshoots with just you.

00:06:36.730 --> 00:06:39.607 position:50% align:center
Today was so exhausting.

00:06:39.691 --> 00:06:42.360 position:50% align:center
Yeah, it was a lot,
but I had so much fun.

00:06:43.945 --> 00:06:46.031 position:50% align:center
I'm glad we did
this group shoot.

00:06:54.164 --> 00:06:55.915 position:50% align:center
Uh, yeah. Me too.

00:06:55.999 --> 00:06:58.960 position:50% align:center
I mean, I guess it
wasn't the worst thing.

00:06:59.044 --> 00:07:02.630 position:50% align:center
Maybe someday,
I might like to try it again.

00:07:06.009 --> 00:07:06.760 position:50% align:center
Hey.

00:07:06.843 --> 00:07:07.802 position:50% align:center
[MARIN]
Omigosh, Gojo!

00:07:07.886 --> 00:07:09.679 position:50% align:center
Did Shinju send
you the files yet?

00:07:09.763 --> 00:07:11.181 position:50% align:center
I'm dying over here!

00:07:11.264 --> 00:07:13.224 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA] They're amazing;
I'm looking at them right now.

00:07:13.308 --> 00:07:15.018 position:50% align:center
[MARIN]
I know, right?

00:07:15.101 --> 00:07:17.187 position:50% align:center
I'm so frikkin hyped about 'em
that I'm watching <i>Blaze</i> again!

00:07:17.270 --> 00:07:18.813 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
For the 800th time.

00:07:18.897 --> 00:07:20.398 position:50% align:center
[MARIN]
