doing dude-makeup?

00:07:23.026 --> 00:07:24.486 position:50% align:center
You are a god!

00:07:24.569 --> 00:07:27.280 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA] I just read a magazine
on how to do cosplay makeup.

00:07:27.364 --> 00:07:28.365 position:50% align:center
[MARIN]
Yeah, I've read 'em, too,

00:07:28.448 --> 00:07:30.241 position:50% align:center
and I can't do what you did.

00:07:30.325 --> 00:07:32.327 position:50% align:center
Juju was super cute as per uzhe.

00:07:32.410 --> 00:07:36.039 position:50% align:center
But Shinju was so hot,
I almost died, it was the best.

00:07:36.122 --> 00:07:38.541 position:50% align:center
And I totes called it on
Shinju wanting to cosplay.

00:07:38.625 --> 00:07:40.210 position:50% align:center
It was awesome
seeing her let loose,

00:07:40.293 --> 00:07:41.670 position:50% align:center
and it seemed like she had fun.

00:07:41.753 --> 00:07:43.004 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Yeah, it did.

00:07:43.088 --> 00:07:44.214 position:50% align:center
Lots of fun.

00:07:44.297 --> 00:07:45.924 position:50% align:center
[MARIN] That's totally
your uniform, isn't it?

00:07:46.007 --> 00:07:47.509 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
It is.

00:07:47.592 --> 00:07:53.390 position:50% align:center
When she told me how she felt,
I couldn't help but relate.

00:07:53.473 --> 00:07:54.641 position:50% align:center
So yeah.

00:07:54.724 --> 00:07:56.184 position:50% align:center
That's why I wanted to help her.

00:07:56.267 --> 00:07:58.603 position:50% align:center
[MARIN] Wait, are you saying
you want to cosplay, too?

00:07:58.687 --> 00:07:59.813 position:50% align:center
