00:07:59.896 --> 00:08:01.773 position:50% align:center
You've got some
'splainin' to do.

00:08:01.856 --> 00:08:03.108 position:50% align:center
I'm hurt, bro.

00:08:03.191 --> 00:08:05.485 position:50% align:center
Like I'd ever make fun of
your sweet Gojo dreams.

00:08:05.568 --> 00:08:07.904 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA] Thanks,
but that's not what I meant.

00:08:07.987 --> 00:08:09.489 position:50% align:center
Also, I had no idea

00:08:09.572 --> 00:08:12.367 position:50% align:center
that you were even building that
Soma cosplay, you little ninja!

00:08:12.450 --> 00:08:13.576 position:50% align:center
When did you plan that?

00:08:13.660 --> 00:08:15.161 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Not long ago, actually.

00:08:15.245 --> 00:08:17.122 position:50% align:center
It was right after
we went to see the studio.

00:08:17.205 --> 00:08:20.583 position:50% align:center
She came over and we
started planning that night.

00:08:20.667 --> 00:08:21.835 position:50% align:center
[NEON'S FLOWER PET]
That's not true, Neon!

00:08:21.918 --> 00:08:23.169 position:50% align:center
You can't give up now!

00:08:23.253 --> 00:08:25.422 position:50% align:center
The three of you have been
best friends forever!

00:08:25.505 --> 00:08:26.715 position:50% align:center
That's what I thought, too.

00:08:26.798 --> 00:08:28.800 position:50% align:center
But I was wrong.

00:08:28.883 --> 00:08:30.135 position:50% align:center
It's done.

00:08:30.218 --> 00:08:32.137 position:50% align:center
After seeing the way those
two look at each other.

00:08:32.220 --> 00:08:33.388 position:50% align:center
Just you two?

00:08:33.471 --> 00:08:34.889 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Yes.

00:08:34.973 --> 00:08:37.475 position:50% align:center
And she was so embarrassed
she asked me not to tell anyone.

00:08:37.559 --> 00:08:38.601 position:50% align:center
[NEON]
Honestly. I'm a fool.

00:08:38.685 --> 00:08:41.354 position:50% align:center
[MARIN]
Oh, 'kay. I get it now.

00:08:41.438 --> 00:08:42.856 position:50% align:center
It all makes sense.

00:08:42.939 --> 00:08:45.650 position:50% align:center
Mm-hm. Sure does.

00:08:48.820 --> 00:08:49.779 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Are you still there?

00:08:49.863 --> 00:08:52.032 position:50% align:center
Kitagawa? Is something wrong?

00:08:52.115 --> 00:08:53.700 position:50% align:center
[MARIN]
No, why do you ask?

00:08:53.783 --> 00:08:56.161 position:50% align:center
Why would anything be wrong?

00:10:30.046 --> 00:10:31.965 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA yawns]

00:10:32.048 --> 00:10:35.135 position:50% align:center
Summer vacation's the greatest!

00:10:35.218 --> 00:10:37.053 position:50% align:center
So much time all to myself!

00:10:37.137 --> 00:10:38.513 position:50% align:center
I can practice
painting doll faces

00:10:38.596 --> 00:10:40.640 position:50% align:center
and then build the next cosplay!

00:11:02.704 --> 00:11:04.080 position:50% align:center
[MARIN]
Okay that's her!

00:11:04.164 --> 00:11:06.041 position:50% align:center
Veronica, my love!

00:11:06.124 --> 00:11:07.709 position:50% align:center
I just can't!

00:11:07.792 --> 00:11:09.794 position:50% align:center
How can anyone not be
obsessed with her?

